com.tractrac.ResultAPI
Class MarkResultItem

java.lang.Object
  com.tractrac.ResultAPI.MarkResultItem

public class MarkResultItem
extends java.lang.Object

Contains all information about a mark-rounding per competitor per mark. Note that not all elements are relevant for the start mark.
